/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T12:20:32.000Z","msg":"普巴呢類nigga一D法國激情浪漫氣息都無，只係土豪暴發戶，質素係咁上下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T12:30:10.000Z","msg":"如果係基沙文講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好想射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:22:55.000Z","msg":"在通道上，基沙文閉上雙眼，望天打卦。突然，他感到一股電流各從五臟六腑激發，匯聚於靈魂深處。是的，這是法國大革命先賢發出的一契靈刃！基沙文腦海閃影出革命之時，志士仁人攻打巴士的監獄之場景；他懷緬著法蘭西民族之光榮事蹟，不禁屈膝長跪，情不自禁地開其金喉，唱出《馬賽進行曲》。唱畢，他高聲疾呼：「今夜，就令我等以自由平等博愛之名，擊殺球皇美斯。復我大法蘭西共榮圈！」他狠勁地睜開雙眼，竟然目見通道上只空剩一人，他是教練迪甘斯！曾祖父於法國大革命捐驅的迪甘斯，以其強勁臂彎扶起基沙文。此時此刻，他倆執手相看淚眼，他倆誓要激倒以美斯為首的帝國主義強弩之末阿根廷。兩人昂首闊步，步出球場，法國一眾隊員卻對兩人報以恥笑的眼光。"},{"pid":"7d9d792d5080b796ad52094304a61cc3fbe40394","tid":747501,"uid":43861,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:35:55.000Z","msg":"基沙文：贏左今晚打fortnite🤙🏻"},{"pid":"bc3eb3e1b4e6247e573ca46dbeaa8b8b8ff39c4e","tid":747501,"uid":124741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:38:25.000Z","msg":"講美斯有咩好笑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd8f48b1d9d02b9ea720cd56a0f8f216aa6efe0","tid":747501,"uid":90422,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:38:30.000Z","msg":"點解首歌要講美斯唔係講牙朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e89587f92115d9defcf63d1040c43f8df927e9","tid":747501,"uid":294,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:41:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XkDUOHLVuII\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXkDUOHLVuII&d=e18W%2Be2xcDlblVKEWQ0FAARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=01e71117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XkDUOHLVuII</a>"},{"pid":"66fad4d0fcaaa639dd2d4d39b0150a9cb9fdb6d3","tid":747501,"uid":84308,"like":30,